02:42.205 --> 02:43.456
Jack!

02:43.539 --> 02:44.582
You know of me?

02:44.666 --> 02:46.292
Of course I do.

02:46.376 --> 02:47.919
I'm magic.

02:48.503 --> 02:51.964
(ROARING)

02:52.048 --> 02:53.508
(SIZZLING)

02:53.758 --> 02:56.552
Magical, isn't it?

02:57.220 --> 03:02.141
You've come for a magic wish, haven't you?

03:02.558 --> 03:04.352
Yes. I...

03:12.110 --> 03:13.403
It's not that simple.

03:13.903 --> 03:18.574
You see, only one of us
is the real Magic Worm.

03:18.866 --> 03:21.619
(LAUGHING MISCHIEVOUSLY)

03:22.078 --> 03:24.455
And you're going
to have to guess...

03:24.539 --> 03:25.790
Which one...

03:25.873 --> 03:27.500
