03:27.583 --> 03:29.127
Then I get my magic wish?

03:29.210 --> 03:31.295
Not quite...

03:31.379 --> 03:32.672
Big boy.

03:32.755 --> 03:37.677
Either one you choose gets to eat you.

03:37.760 --> 03:40.096
Eat me? What magic is that?

03:40.179 --> 03:42.014
Let me explain.

03:42.390 --> 03:47.687
If you guess right,
you will be transported to a magical place

03:47.812 --> 03:51.941
where your innermost
desire will be granted.

03:52.900 --> 03:58.698
But if you guess wrong,
you'll be digested for 500 years.

04:00.324 --> 04:03.161
(LAUGHING)

04:03.453 --> 04:05.163
So all I have to do is guess?

04:05.246 --> 04:06.748
MALE WORM: That's right.

04:06.831 --> 04:08.750
No, wrong.

04:09.333 --> 04:12.211
You have to play a little game.

04:12.503 --> 04:14.672
Smashing idea.

04:14.839 --> 04:17.008
Oh, jolly.

04:20.094 --> 04:21.095
Knock! Knock!

04:23.514 --> 04:26.267
You're supposed to
say, "Who's there?"

04:26.768 --> 04:28.728
Uh, who is there?

04:28.811 --> 04:29.854
Banana.

04:30.104 --> 04:31.230
Uh...

04:31.564 --> 04:34.484
Now you say, "Banana who?"

04:34.776 --> 04:36.152
Knock! Knock!

04:36.235 --> 04:37.320
Uh, who is there?

04:37.403 --> 04:39.071
- Banana.
- Banana who?

04:39.155 --> 04:40.281
Knock! Knock!

04:40.364 --> 04:41.532
- Who is there?
- Banana.

04:41.616 --> 04:42.742
Banana who?

04:42.825 --> 04:46.287
No, wait. Scratch that. Try again.

04:46.746 --> 04:47.830
Knock! Knock!

04:49.707 --> 04:50.750
Who's there?

04:50.833 --> 04:54.170
Now you're asking the questions.

04:56.339 --> 04:58.299
Okay, you start.

04:58.382 --> 05:00.426
Uh, knock, knock.

05:00.510 --> 05:02.595
BOTH: Who's there?

05:03.513 --> 05:06.557
Uh... Er... Uh...

05:06.641 --> 05:11.187
- Enough!
- Okay, we'll ask you a question.

05:11.771 --> 05:15.066
What's your favorite color?

05:15.149 --> 05:16.526
What trick is this?

05:16.609 --> 05:18.069
No trick.

05:18.152 --> 05:19.278
Answer it!

05:19.362 --> 05:21.113
(LAUGHING)

05:21.447 --> 05:23.032
- Blue?
- BOTH: Wrong!

05:23.115 --> 05:26.244
I mean red. Red. Hmph.

05:26.327 --> 05:27.411
Too late.

05:27.495 --> 05:29.163
Final question.

05:29.247 --> 05:30.456
Very well.

05:30.540 --> 05:33.668
One of us tells only lies.

05:33.751 --> 05:36.045
The other tells only truths.

05:36.128 --> 05:39.257
By asking us only one question...

05:39.340 --> 05:42.718
You must decide which
is the real Magic Worm.

05:43.010 --> 05:44.387
(GRIPPING INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC PLAYING)

05:48.182 --> 05:50.726
Only one!

06:22.967 --> 06:25.011
My question will be...

06:25.094 --> 06:26.804
