06:27.263 --> 06:31.893
If you were your brother,
which one would you say is the Magic Worm?

06:34.186 --> 06:36.230
Which one are you asking?

06:36.439 --> 06:37.648
It doesn't matter.

06:37.732 --> 06:39.525
Hmm...

06:40.192 --> 06:42.111
That's easy. It's him.

06:42.486 --> 06:44.655
Of course. It's me.

06:45.197 --> 06:47.533
Then I choose you!

06:47.617 --> 06:48.659
He knows!

06:49.243 --> 06:50.870
What makes you choose me?

06:50.953 --> 06:52.330
I told you it was him.

06:52.413 --> 06:53.873
Yes. Me!

06:53.956 --> 06:56.417
If you were the truth-telling Worm,
then what you said would be a lie,

06:56.500 --> 06:58.961
because you will answer truthfully
what your lying brother will say.

06:59.045 --> 07:00.796
Therefore, I can safely say that
the answer will be

07:00.880 --> 07:02.048
the opposite of what you say.

07:02.131 --> 07:03.674
On the other hand,
if you are the lying Worm,

07:03.758 --> 07:05.593
then you will tell me
what your truth-telling brother will say,

07:05.676 --> 07:06.677
but it would be a lie.

07:06.761 --> 07:08.804
Therefore, the answer
will also be the opposite of what <i>you</i> say.

07:09.597 --> 07:10.806
Understand?

07:10.890 --> 07:12.767
